{
  "stem": "365.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And like a fool, I gave him my name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I told him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They probably caught him with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he told them, probably, that he bought it from me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From this, they will string me up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I says, till now luck stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Eventually, my luck ran out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That is the first thing going through my mind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he just sizes me up, looks at me, and doesn't say another word.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He lifts up the list and calls another guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I think to myself, well, at least if there is going to be a necktie party, I'll have company.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I won't be alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He calls a third.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He calls a fourth-- calls out 10 guys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We look at each other-- all the 10 that used to work in the Organisation Todt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Out of the 30, exactly 10 survived. 20 died during the epidemic. 2/3 of the camp died in the epidemic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Out of 3,000, 1,000 remained.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He turns around to the chief of the prisoners-- the altester.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He says, send them to the showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Give them clean clothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They are going back to the Organisation Todt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Now, that was paradise after that work-- for two reasons-- easier work-- not as hard-- and a supply of food-- that is, if you are lucky-- [LAUGHS] if you are not caught in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Anyways, the next day, we go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In the meantime, they had German workers that they employed already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We are put to work there again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm put to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There again, they send me to-- do the accounting-- various.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I do the accounting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "At one time, when the Germans are working, the Germans-- I got to explain that episode-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] The Germans are loading.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We received a shipment of wooden shoes, or boots, from Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
